title: Bug 7945 - Search results not selected in external jar
description:
The search results in the external jar are not selected in Build 200201151. When searching for references to a field, only one match is shown. 

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Launch the application.
2. Open the search functionality.
3. Search for references to the field.

Observed Behavior:
Double-clicking on the search result does not select it.

Expected Behavior:
When searching for references to the field, there should be 3 matches. Double-clicking on a search result should select it.
